OL,5, A 12-year-old boy who died after a     
OL,6, paranoid schizophrenic drove into a    
OL,7, crowd of schoolchildren was let down by
OL,8, a police force, its commissioner said. 
OL,10,FHarley Watson was hit outside Debden   
OL,11,FPark High School in Loughton, Essex, on
OL,12,F2 December 2019.                       
OL,14,FTerence Glover, 52, was detained       
OL,15,Findefinitely under the Mental Health   
OL,16,FAct last year.                         
OL,18,FPolice, fire and crime commissioner for
OL,19,FEssex, Roger Hirst, said "much more    
OL,20,Fcould and should have been done".      
